title: Man dynamic que is great

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: The only premade were the "El"'s. How the hell did these sub level 30's get matched up aganst a Silver 2, A Gold 1 (Season 5 Plat) and a Silver 3?

replies.body: Well, I was playing with high silvers and low golds before I was level 30, so maybe these guys are just good at the game and good at playing normals.
This seems to be a normal game. And in normal games these things happen often. Nothing special about it
But it's just absurd how arbitrary this is.
